{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 7,
  "title": "第七章（无私）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "天長地久。天地之所以能長且久者，以亓不自生也，故能長生。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人，芮亓身而身先，外亓身而身存。"
    },
    {
      "text": "不以亓无私與，故能成亓私。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 28,
          "end": 28
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天地所以獨長且久者，以其安靜，施不求報，不如人居處，汲汲求自饒之利，奪人以自與也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 25,
          "end": 26
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以其不求生，故能長生不終也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 19,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先人而後己也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 14,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天下敬之，先以為長。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 19,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "薄己而厚人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 22,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "百姓愛之如父母，神明祐之若赤子，故身常存。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 13,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人為人所愛，神明所祐，非以其公正無私所致乎。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 24,
          "end": 25
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人以為私者，欲以厚己也。聖人無私而己自厚，故能成其私也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 28,
          "end": 28
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "自生則與物爭，不自生則物歸也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 13,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無私者，無為於身也。身先身存，故曰，能成其私也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
